{
  "stem": "142.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Half of it was the Germans, and from Larissa down to southern Greece, the Italians occupied then.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they put us in a school where we stayed there until I was caught by the Germans in the synagogue in March, 1944.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Before we get to that, while you were still in Salonika, before you left, were the Germans that were there treating the Greek Jews differently than the Italian Jews?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- they didn't-- they didn't do us-- We had in our door, we had from Italian-- from the Italian consulate a piece of paper that we're Italians.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Jews, they didn't touch us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't do anything, even though that they were complaining to the Italian authorities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Italian government said that they shouldn't touch us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were- they were doing-- you know, little by little, they were putting in ghettos.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they-- I didn't see too much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I saw when they start taking them, you know, because I had a lot of friends of mine, you know, they went from Salonika.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Friends from school and-- and regular young friends of mine that they were taken.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they started transports.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was already-- when they start taking them I was already in Athens.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, went along.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but I-- when I was in Athens, you know-- but there were always Jewish traitors around the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you know, they saved themselves for a while, but at the end they all perished.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was in-- in 1943.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
